  "detailed_description": "Rabbit hole is a mystery adventure game.<br><br>One day, Alice opens her eyes in an unknown place called Rabbit Hall House. All she sees in front of her eyes is a letter reading \"Invitation to Rabbithole Games\"… And Alice will find out soon. Rabbithole game is a killing game that kills each other. There's only one winner.<br><br>Only those who survive this brutal killing game can be the winners of Rabbit Hall House games.<br>How far can you survive?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game inspired by Alice in Wonderland</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>7 individual characters.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Collect clues through NPCs and objects</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A mystery game using collected clues</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shocking truth revealed as the ending approaches</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Rabbit hole is a mystery adventure game.<br><br>One day, Alice opens her eyes in an unknown place called Rabbit Hall House. All she sees in front of her eyes is a letter reading \"Invitation to Rabbithole Games\"… And Alice will find out soon. Rabbithole game is a killing game that kills each other. There's only one winner.<br><br>Only those who survive this brutal killing game can be the winners of Rabbit Hall House games.<br>How far can you survive?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game inspired by Alice in Wonderland</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>7 individual characters.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Collect clues through NPCs and objects</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A mystery game using collected clues</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shocking truth revealed as the ending approaches</li></ul>",
